{"tid":1369894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日黎元朗買老婆餅追星既手足，留意元朗一樣特色既野","createTime":"2019-07-26T22:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:52.000Z","uid":2161,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb281f1ce3db899bb6bc4d32515c39254d24b5f3","tid":1369894,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:18:11.000Z","msg":"你地追星還追星，買老婆餅還老婆餅<br />\n我地大西北依賴輕鐵做交通工具架<br />\n而元朗好容易就會見到路軌上面啲石仔<br />\n佢既作用係用黎減震。你地只可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">近距離觀賞，不可以執走</span></span><br />\n唔係會令到我地最愛香港市民同以市民為主既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵附屬既輕鐵元朗路段癱喚架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然如果遇到惡佈分子/受到不對等襲擊拎黎自衛都唔錯架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f84665f98188036cc20a84eb623dac43c6635d5","tid":1369894,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:18:59.000Z","msg":"推到手足可以欣賞到元朗特色同埋少少自衛既本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21cb006145af42fd993d7f7e0b78b721f9bd74b","tid":1369894,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:19:43.000Z","msg":"推到手足可以欣賞到元朗特色同埋少少保護自己既本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396902bb77e7680748806d232802320907b14835","tid":1369894,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:21:36.000Z","msg":"推到手足可以欣賞到元朗特色同埋少少保護自己既本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95c0429e46d8f99604625b870d2ded05e336ddd","tid":1369894,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:25:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cda31853494b5d2007bdaae20b521a249c617af","tid":1369894,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-la